<p>
	It&#39;s true, the <a href="http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/stat?id=p8StJ7oxYpg&amp;offerid=146261&amp;type=3&amp;subid=0&amp;tmpid=1826&amp;RD_PARM1=http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fus%252Fapp%252Fmac-geek-gab%252Fid551440150%253Fmt%253D8%2526uo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" data-wpel-link="external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Mac Geek Gab iOS App</a> is out! Hear all about it from John and Dave, plus, of course, all your questions answered, Cool Stuff Found, and much, much more. You can&#39;t beat this, folks. Download the episode today (it&#39;s free, as always) and enjoy!</p>
